    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐贯穿整个Rhapsody星球，从蓝草草地到崎岖的山脉。它支撑着神秘的AlgoRhythm，现在面临来自超自然力量驱使的生物的威胁。作为一个失败的外星流行乐队，你可能没有达到顶峰，但你有勇气和节奏来拯救你的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/39871c1d3fb3a3f960dbf6db5db3ddda.poster.avif?t=1770744814\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/39871c1d3fb3a3f960dbf6db5db3ddda.webm?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/39871c1d3fb3a3f960dbf6db5db3ddda.mp4?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由音乐构建</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次试玩版包含教程和三个关卡，涵盖嘻哈、Tech House 和 Drum 'n' Bass。每个关卡都有动态的音乐，随着你放置的塔楼而不断演变。运用战略性塔楼布局，感受音乐的变化，指挥你的防御战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/bb27e2883eb6d34899fa1bd3b30c2755.poster.avif?t=1770744814\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/bb27e2883eb6d34899fa1bd3b30c2755.webm?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/bb27e2883eb6d34899fa1bd3b30c2755.mp4?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >节奏和塔防的完美和谐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用策略有效地定位和升级你的节奏塔。随着音乐强度的增加，你的塔的力量也随之增强。当你穿越外星景观时，解锁新的塔楼，回应你的节奏影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4dc97bf0a66a25dd78119a44f08df417.poster.avif?t=1770744814\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4dc97bf0a66a25dd78119a44f08df417.webm?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4dc97bf0a66a25dd78119a44f08df417.mp4?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在合作模式下一起即兴创作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本地合作模式中邀请朋友一起游戏。你们会分割地图，各自守护自己的领土？还是一人建塔，一人减缓敌人前进？患难见真情！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4a1d4d93b884f1c99d2f3aecb074a1fd.poster.avif?t=1770744814\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4a1d4d93b884f1c99d2f3aecb074a1fd.webm?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1703240/extras/4a1d4d93b884f1c99d2f3aecb074a1fd.mp4?t=1770744814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用疯狂的敌人提高节奏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接讨厌节奏的敌人的浪潮，每个敌人都有独特的模式和弱点。演示版通过boss挑战你的策略和节奏技能到极限。适应和发展你的战术，以克服这些新威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的星球充满音乐。感受它，建造它，在这个功能丰富的试玩版中享受节奏吧！支持单人模式和本地合作模式！</p>",
